overview: Five Horror Film in one Movie. This local horror film features Mak Jah, Sura Sojangi, Kalpana, Sundraju, Naqia Nasution, Khatijah Tan, Zul Yasmin and more talented cast. The film is a production from RenBash Entertainment with M.Subash as the director.
tagline: Five Horror Story In One Movie
title: Mistik Syirik Tahyul
